        scenario: 'You have 500 promoter sequences (2kb upstream of TSS) from a set of co-expressed genes. A ChIP-seq experiment identified a putative motif for a novel transcription factor. You need to scan all promoters for this motif, identify high-scoring matches, and summarize the results with GC content and consensus analysis.',
